---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section 
  id="story"
  title="The Legend Begins"
  subtitle="Discover the origin story of Super Nigga"
  backgroundColor="bg-black"
>
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-5xl">
    <!-- Story Content -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-left">
      <div class="bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-yellow-400">Chapter 1: The Awakening</h3>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          In the depths of the digital realm, a new hero emerged. Super Nigga wasn't just born—he was forged in the fires of innovation and community spirit.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          With powers beyond imagination and a mission to revolutionize the crypto space, our hero began his journey to unite communities and create lasting value.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-400">Chapter 2: The Mission</h3>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Super Nigga's mission is clear: to create a decentralized ecosystem where every holder becomes part of something greater. A community-driven token with real utility and purpose.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Visual Elements -->
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl blur-xl opacity-30"></div>
        <div class="relative bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/20">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Powers & Abilities</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>Community Building</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>Value Creation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>Innovation Drive</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>Decentralization</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400">∞</div>
          <div class="text-sm opacity-80">Potential</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">100%</div>
          <div class="text-sm opacity-80">Community</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>